name: FNF In Smoke Em' Out Struggle Return of Garcello - HD
name_original: FNF In Smoke Em' Out Struggle Return of Garcello - HD
description: A game about Garcello's return to the real world after dying because of cigarettes and smoke.  I guess he wanted more...? Remastered in HD,  along with (possibly) new updates, here is: FNF In Smoke Em' Out Struggle  Return of Garcello - HD!
